name: Voyage marketers
overview:
Voyage Marketer’s pvt. Ltd. was established in 1999 under the companies act,1956. The most current project the Voyage Marketers involved is promoting the health portal www.healthplus24.com.

healthplus24.com is a source for free, comprehensive medical information on the web and it is a unique bland of the concept of social networking and health information. Here people can interact with the other users and share their personal and health information. They can also get expert advice on various symptoms or prescriptions.
The directors have the expertise in the filed health care and software development. The voyage marketers have various plans to implement in near future after successfully promoting the health portal.
